com.kontakt.sdk.android.connection

Interface BeaconConnection.WriteListener

  • Enclosing class:
    BeaconConnection

    public static interface BeaconConnection.WriteListener
    WriteListener provides callbacks indicating whether Beacon characteristics manipulation ended successfully or failed.
